column1: #Text=Brazilian surfer wins world championship in Pichilemu , Chile
#Text=Attendants to the Quiksilver ceremonial , looking forwards to the Punta de Lobos rocks .
#Text=The fourteenth Quiksilver Ceremonial Punta de Lobos Big Wave Invitational surf championship took place on Saturday in the Chilean city of Pichilemu , often called the " Capital of the Surf .
